{"tid":1153432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個二個反共都做埋哂啲冇建設性嘅野","createTime":"2019-05-13T15:24:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T17:03:56.000Z","uid":241832,"like":15,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6bde9ed72b6241ce8f1a177a2037e2d12314fb9","tid":1153432,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"要反都做啲有建設性啲啦<br />\n你老尾睇套大陸劇娛樂下都要比你屌<br />\n就算全部人都唔睇對反支都完全冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反共第一步就係show blocked user<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好撚成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個時勢明顯好難鬥 <br />\n連侵侵都咁驚支那<br />\n證明佢有一定威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要革命就要犧牲<br />\n一個二個show blocked user咁撚堅<br />\n不如召喚連登巴打出去一刀一個<br />\n坐完出嚟就封你為革命義士<br />\n得個講字同抵制支那就覺得自己反緊共<br />\n你就收收你皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5600698a6c8258a619f2e04bddb01a38aa106db8","tid":1153432,"uid":241832,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e6bde9ed72b6241ce8f1a177a2037e2d12314fb9","tid":1153432,"uid":241832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T15:24:18.000Z","msg":"要反都做啲有建設性啲啦<br />\n你老尾睇套大陸劇娛樂下都要比你屌<br />\n就算全部人都唔睇對反支都完全冇幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反共第一步就係show blocked user<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你好撚成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個時勢明顯好難鬥 <br />\n連侵侵都咁驚支那<br />\n證明佢有一定威脅<img src=\"/assets/